<p>Use the menu to signup, and then navigate,<br/>
    via search -> List to find piles in a category</p>
<p>To find card to learn click here</p>
<%= link_to '<img src="/images/buttons/Search.png" width="100" height="36" alt="Category Search" />',:controller => 'search' %><br />
<p class="boxsmall">
<b><big><font color = "red" >
    Please note, ReCALL is in development.<br />
    If you find a problem/error,<br/>
    so please contact the webmaster via mail<br />
 <a href="mailto:webmaster (AT) mednote (DOT) dk"><img
        src="/images/webmasterATmednoteDK_r.png" alt="Webmaster e-mail" height="21" width="220" /></a>
